latestPosts.caption:
My go to summer makeup🌞🧴⛱️ ✨ 
Lock in your makeup by following these simple steps🧡
.
.
🌻Step 1 : @dotandkey.skincare moisturiser 
🌻Step 2: @aqualogica.in sunscreen 
🌻Step 3: @anastasiabeverlyhills setting spray 
🌻Step 4: @reachedmars powder 
🌻Step 5: @insightcosmetic primer 
Wait for few seconds in between each steps🫶

Use a very little foundation or a tinted moisturiser 
@maybellinearabia fresh tint
Or you can completely avoid this step & spot conceal @maybelline fitme concealer 
Switch to cream or liquid blushes @officialswissbeauty blush
On my lips: 
@reachedmars lipliner 
@mynykaa @nysaamiddleeast lipstick-you’re latte

Hijab: @ta_rooha 🤎
